# Слои бэкенда

Только бэкенд. BC-first на **каждом** слое.

## Дерево

```
app/
├── Shared/ValueObject/          # Phone, Email, Money, EntityId
├── Domain/{BC}/
│   ├── Entity/ ValueObject/ Enum/
│   ├── Repository/              # ports
│   └── Service/
├── Application/{BC}/
│   ├── Command/ CommandHandler/
│   ├── Query/ QueryHandler/
│   └── Presenter/
├── Infrastructure/{BC}/
│   ├── Persistence/Eloquent|Mapper|Repository/
│   └── Auth/                    # где нужно
└── Infrastructure/Shared/Provider/
```

## Зависимости

Presentation → Application → Domain ← Infrastructure
Shared — без BC-семантики

## Cross-BC

- Domain: только `*_id`
- Orchestration: Application/{BC}/CommandHandler

## DI

`App\Infrastructure\Shared\Provider\PersistenceServiceProvider`
